dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Reprinted 1943 by A.M.S. 2-43. 113599. Military grid (brown). "Grid provisional." Important buildings are named. North Italy Grid - Convergence - Grid North is 01°31ʹW. of True North on this sheet. United States. Army Map Service Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4380 In upper margin: Italy. "Copied from an Italian plan dated 1935". Northern Italy grid. Convergence: Grid north is 1-degree 31' W of True North on this sheet.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
